\v 20 \x - \xo 27:20 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 30:16; Habakuk 2:5\x*Gumazamizir bar av…®riba ovegha g…®fa. Ez…® Oveaghuezibar Nguibam, gumazamiziba a giz…®vaghan kogham. Gumazamiziba oveng…®v…®ra ikiam. Kamagh…®ra, gumazamiziba bizibagh ifueghamin arazim iz…®vaghan kogh, kamagh…®ra ik…®v…®ra ikiam.
