\v 1 \x - \xo 28:1 \xt Ofa Gami 26:17; 26:36; Onger Akaba 53:5\x*Gumazir arazir kurabagh amiba puram atiatia aragharui. Ez…® gumazir aghuiba laionbar m…®n tuiva gavgavigha atiatir puvat…®.
