\v 4 \x - \xo 28:4 \xt 1 Atriviba 18:18; 18:21; Efesus 5:11\x*Gumazamiziba ak…®rim ragha God…®n Akar Gavgavibagh asara, me gumazir arazir kurabagh amibar ziaba fe. Ez…® gumazamizir God…®n Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zuiba, me gumazir kuraba pamten me d…®kab…®ri.
