\v 13 \x - \xo 28:13 \xt Onger Akaba 32:3-5; 1 Jon 1:8-10\x*Gumazim uan arazir kuram modogh, an amir ingangaritam deragh otoghan kogham. Ez…® gumazim uan arazir kuraba bar da ghurigh, ak…®rim ragh arazir kurar kabagh asaraght…®, God an apangkuvigham.
