\v 18 \x - \xo 29:18 \xt 1 Samuel 3:1; Amos 8:11-12\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akam gumazamizibagh an…®ngizir puvat…®z…®, me tintinibar arazir igharazir av…®rim gamighai. Ez…® gumazir God…®n Akar Gavgavibar g…®n zuim, a bar akongegham.
