\v 5 God…®n akam, a bar guizbang…®ra. Ez…® bizir a damuasa m…®geiba, da bar guiz…®n otifi. Egha a bar deraghav…®ra gumazamizir a bagha zuiba, d…®vazim…®n m…®n me av…®nigha men gari, mati oram, m…®dorozir gumaziba modorozim…®n ghua an suigha uarir p…®si.
\v 6 Eght…® n…® God…®n akam gis…®n, uab…® uan akam isafuragh an gun m…®k…®mam, egh suam, kar God…®n akamra. N…® kamagh…®n damut…®, a n…®n atar n…® ak…®right…®, g…®n gumazamiziba fogh suam, n…® gumazir ifarim.
