\v 7 O God, k…® bizir pumuning bagha n…®n azangasa, eght…® n…® na dan…®ngasa k…® ifonge. K…® nguazim…®n ikiamin dughiam…®n,
\v 8 \x - \xo 30:8 \xt Matyu 6:11; Luk 11:3\x*\x - \xo 30:8-9 \xt Nehemia 9:25-26; Jop 31:24; Hosea 13:6\x*n…® nan akuraght…®, k…® ak…®rim ragh ifavarir arazibagh asaragham. Eght…® n…® na ateght…®, k…® dag…®aba iz…®vazir gumazim…®n m…®n otivan kogh, egh uaghan onganarazibagh amir gumazim…®n m…®n otivan kogham. N…® dughiar vam…®ran vaghvagh daghebara na dan…®ng.
\v 9 Guizbang…®ra, k…® dagher av…®riba ik…®va, ak…®rim ragh n…® gasaragh egh m…®k…®m suam, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a tinara?‚Äù Egh k…® onganarazibagh amir gumazim…®n m…®n otogh…®va, ti ok…®m…®va uan God…®n ziam d…®kab…®ragham.
\p 
\v 10 N…® gumazir dapanim bagh mang…® g…®rak…®rang…®n an ingangarir gumazitam m…®k…®man mark…®. N…® kamagh…®n damut…®, ingangarir gumazim God ko m…®k…®mt…®, a paz…® n…® damight…®, n…® os…®mt…®zim inigham.
\p 
\v 11 Gumazamizir maba ghaze, ‚ÄúGod paz…®v…®ra men amebaba ko afeziabar amuam.‚Äù
\v 12 \x - \xo 30:12 \xt 1 Jon 1:8\x*Ez…® gumazamizir maba ghaze, ‚ÄúMe arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®.‚Äù Ez…® puvat…®, men arazir kuram…®n os…®mt…®zim ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® me God…®n damazim…®n bar m…®ze.
\v 13 Ez…® gumazamizir maba uan ziaba fa ghaze, e bar deraz…®, gumazir igharaziba me pura biziba.
\v 14 Ez…® gumazamizir maba bar pazav…®ra onganarazibagh amir gumazamizibagh ami. Men atariba mati sababa ko afuaba men akabagh iz…®vaz…®ma, me onganarazibagh amir gumazamizibagh amua bar me ag…®vasa.
