\v 15 Ghuziba apir m…®k…®nbam a guivir pumuning iti, ez…® aning kamagh…®n arai, ‚ÄúNa Dan…®ng, na Dan…®ng.‚Äù
\p Guizbang…®ra, 4plan bizir kaba men ifongiaba g…®vaghan kogham:
\b
\li1 
\v 16 Kar, Gumazamizir Oveaghuezibar Nguibam,
\li1 ko amizir furabar itim,
