\b
\p 
\v 17 Gumazitam uan amebam ko afeziam…®n akam batuegh, d…®bovir akabar aning m…®k…®m, egh aremeghamin dughiam…®n, me an kuam afaghan kogham. Eght…® kuarazir kotkotba an damazimning asight…®, kuarazir isaba an m…®karzim amegham.
\p 
\v 18 Kar, 4plan bizir bar igharagha gariba, k…® adagh fozir puvat…®:
\b
\li1 
\v 19 Kar, kuarazir isam p…®n m…®ghagha aruir arazim,
\li1 ko kuruzim dag…®am gis…®n rozir arazim,
\li1 ko kurim ongarim gis…®n aruir arazim,
\li1 ko gumazim amizir igiam gifongezir arazim.
\b
\p 
\v 20 Pam…®n itir amizim, gumazir igharaziba koma akua, egha kamagh…®n ami: a dagheba amegha akam ruegha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®.‚Äù
\p 
\v 21 Arazir 4pla da nguazim…®n otifi. Kar arazir bar kuraba, nguazim uab…® arazir kabar aghuagha, bar puv…®ra ivazvasi.
\v 22 Arazir kaba kamak…®n:
\b
\li1 Ingangarir gumazir k…®nim atrivim…®n otogha amir arazim,
\li1 ko gumazir n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba puvat…®zim puv…®ra apir arazim,
\li1 
\v 23 ko amizir fom…®ra gumaziba a gifongezir puvat…®zim, a dat…®r…®gh…®n pam…®n iti, an arazim,
\li1 ko ingangarir amizim uan amizir dapanim…®n danganim inizir arazim.
\b
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® nguazir kam…®n 4plan as…®ziba ko apizir muziariba ikia, n…®ghn…®zir bar aghuiba iti:
\b
\li1 
\v 25 Sibaba gavgaviba puvat…®gha, me dagheba otevir dughiam bagha, dagheba akuva ada ar…®si.
\li1 
\v 26 Ez…® iriaba uaghan gavgaviba puvat…®gha dag…®ar ekiabar t…®zibar m…®konibar ingari.
\li1 
\v 27 Ez…® odeziba atriviba puvat…®gha me bar uari inigha okoruam…®n arui.
\li1 
\v 28 Ez…® m…®z…®viar muziariba, e uan dafarim…®n dar suigham. Ez…® da atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n iti.
\b
\p 
\v 29 Ez…® 4plan biziba bar ganganir aghuim gamuava arui:
\b
\li1 
\v 30 Laionba bar gavgavigha, bar as…®zir mabagh afira. Egha da arua bizitam…®n atiatir puvat…®.
\li1 
\v 31 Ez…® tuarir apuriba, uan dapaniba fava arui,
\li1 ez…® memen apuriba arui,
\li1 ez…® atrivim a bar gavgavigha arua fo, apanitam a gafiraghan kogham.
\b
\p 
\v 32 N…® arazir onganim gamua ifaghata uab…®ra uan ziam fava, arazir kurabar amuasa n…®ghn…®si. N…® uan akam dukuagh, arazir kam atakigh.
\v 33 N…® fo, n…® bulmakaun oter eborim inigh a gigh…®t…®, bata otogham. Egh n…® gumazir igharazim…®n atinim m…®sueght…®, ghuzim otogham. Kamagh…®ra, n…® gumazamizibar amut…® me atart…®, m…®dorozim otogham.
\c 31
\s1 Atrivim Lemuel…®n akar aghuiba
\p 
\v 1 Kar atrivim Lemuel…®n akaba. An amebam n…®ghn…®zir aghuim a dan…®ngasa akar kam…®n a geghani.
\p 
\v 2 Nan otarim, k…® God…®n azaraz…®, a n…® isa na gan…®ngi. Ez…® k…® uab…® n…® bategha, bar n…® gifonge. Kamagh…®n n…® deraghv…®ra nan akam baragh.
\v 3 N…® amiziba ko ikararang me ko daku uan gavgavim me dan…®ngan mark…®. Guizbang…®ra, kamagh garir amiziba atrivibagh amima me ikufi.
\v 4 O Lemuel, n…® oragh! N…® atriviba, wain…®n d…®pabar aman mark…®, egh d…®par onganir igharagha gariba sara dam…®s…® navim d…®kavan mark…®.
\v 5 Me d…®par onganibar am…®va kantrin araziba g…®n amadagh, uaghan onganarazibagh amir gumazamiziba paz…® me damuam.
\v 6 D…®par onganim ko wain, kar gumazamizir ovengasava amiba ko os…®mt…®zir ekiaba itir gumazamizibar bizimning.
\v 7 Me ifuegh dam…®va, uam onganarazibagh amir dabirabiba ko os…®mt…®zir bar ekiaba dagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.
\p 
\v 8 N…®, gumazamizir uan os…®mt…®zibar gun m…®k…®man koghamibagh n…®ghnigh, kot…®n aven men akuragh m…®k…®m. Egh n…® kot…®n aven m…®k…®m gavgavight…®ma, kot arazir aghuibar onganarazibagh amir gumazamiziba me damu.
\v 9 Egh n…® uab…® kotiam baragh, arazir aghuimra damu. Egh onganarazibagh amir gumazamiziba ko biziba puvat…®zir gumazamizibar akurvagh.
\s1 Amuir aghuim…®n araziba\f + \fr 31:10 \ft Israelian akaba osirir arazim, a mong igharagha ghu. Hibrun akam…®n aven, me 22plan letaba ikia uan akaba osiri. Dughiar maba, me akaba osirasa, 22plan vezba o danganibar me akar kaba vaghvagh dar faragh ikiasa letaba ar…®si. Gumaziba Hibrun akam g…®gha akar igharaziba osirir dughiabar, me zurara Israelian arazir kam…®n g…®n ghua da osirir puvat…®. Hibrun akam…®n aven, Aghuzir Akabar 31:10-31 arazir kam…®n g…®n zui. Hibrun akam…®n arazir kam, danganir vam…®ran itir puvat…®, me danganir igharazir kabar arazir kam…®n g…®n zui: Azirakam 1-4 ko Onger Akaba 9-10 ko 25 ko 34 ko 37 ko 111 ko 119 ko 145.\f*
\p 
\v 10 \x - \xo 31:10 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 12:4; 18:22; 19:14\x*Guizbang…®ra, gumazim ti amizir arazir bar aghuiba itim…®n ik…®s…®, a bar pamtem da buriam. Kamagh…®n garir amizim, a bar deragha p…®n ikia dag…®ar iveziba bar p…®n koziba bar dagh afira.
\p 
\v 11 Amizir kamagh amim, an pam uan navir averiam…®n aven n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an ikia deraghv…®ra a g…®fo, a zuraram arazir aghuibar g…®n zui. Eght…® an amuim an akuraght…®, a bizir av…®riba ikiam.
\p 
\v 12 Amizir kam dughiaba vaghvagha arazir aghuibara, uan pam gami.
\p 
\v 13 Egha a tret…®n aghuir me sipsip…®n ar…®zibar ingariziba, ko tret…®n aghuir igharagha gariba inigha, korotiaba isamasa bar akonge.
\p 
\v 14 Egha a mati kurir ekiaba ami mogh…®n, saghon ghua dagheba isi, kamagh…®n amiz…® an adarazi me dagher av…®riba iti.
\p 
\v 15 Amizir kamagh amim, am…®nim t…®ghar bar tiragham, an osegha d…®kavigha uan pam ko boriba bagha dagheba tue. Egha uan ingangarir amiziba bagha ingangariba ab…®gha me gan…®di.
\p 
\v 16 Amizir kamagh amim, a faragha nguazir mam…®n ganigha derav…®ra n…®ghnigha, a givese. Egha g…®n a uan dag…®ar a faragha iniziba inigha, wain…®n ik…®zim…®n ov…®zibagh ivezegha, da opari.
\p 
\v 17 Amizir kam, dughiatam…®n am…®razir puvat…®. An amizir gavgavir bar puv…®ra ingarim.
\p 
\v 18 Egha an lam munger puvat…®gha isiav…®ra itima, a ingara ghua d…®magarir ar…®zim…®n tu. Egha uan bizibagh amaga dagh ivezir ingangarim…®n garima, a deraghv…®ra zui.
\p 
\v 19 Kamagh amir amizim, uab…® ua bagh tretbagh ir…®gha, inibar ingari.
\p 
\v 20 Egha a gumazamizibar gari, me biziba otevegha onganarazibagh amima, a biziba isa me gan…®di.
\p 
\v 21 Egha a uan pam ko boriba bagha korotiar bar aghuiba isamigha g…®vaz…® da bar deragha iti. Eght…® amozir orangt…®zir dughiam iz…®t…®, a ua korotiaba me bagh dagh n…®ghn…®ghan kogham.
\p 
\v 22 Egha a uab…® uan d…®penim…®n itir dakoziba aver inibar ingari. Egha a inir ghurghurir aghuiba ko inir p…®ghaghevir aghuiba inigha ua bagha korotiaba isai.
\p 
\v 23 Ez…® nguibam…®n gumazir dapaniba ziar ekiam an pam gan…®di. Ez…® an pam men tong…®n uaghan men gumazir dapanir mam.
\p 
\v 24 Ez…® dughiar av…®ribar amizir kam korotiar aghuiba isava, letiabar ingarima, biziba amadir gumazamiziba izava dagh ivesi.
\p 
\v 25 Amizir kam, ziar ekiam ko gavgavim itima, aning mati korotiam…®n m…®n anevara. Egha a bizir g…®n otivambar atiatir puvat…®.
\p 
\v 26 A gumazamizibagh ifuegha men sure gamua, deragha bighav…®ra me m…®gei. Egha an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, da n…®ghn…®zir aghuiba ko fofozir aghuim iti.
\v 27 Egha a uan d…®penim…®n biziba derav…®ra dar gara dagh iporporir puvat…®. A puv…®ra ingara ingangarir aghuim gami.
\p 
\v 28 Ez…® an boriba d…®kavigha uan amebam…®n ziam fava a d…®bora ghaze, ‚ÄúKar en amebar bar aghuimra.‚Äù Ez…® an pam uaghan an ziam fav…®ra ikia ghaze,
\p 
\v 29 ‚ÄúEn nguibam…®n aven amizir av…®riba arazir bar aghuibagh ami, ez…® n…® bar deragha, bar me gafira.‚Äù
\p 
\v 30 Amizitam akar is…®ngt…®ziba e dan…®ngt…®, e foghan kogham, a guizbang…®ra m…®gei o, a ti ifari. Ez…® e fo, amizir ganganir aghuim gamim, a kamagh…®ra ik…®v…®ra ikian kogham. Ez…® amizir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apengan ikia an atiatim, e amizir kam…®n ziam fam.
\p 
\v 31 Bar guizbang…®ra, e amizir kam…®n arazim ko ingangarir aghuir an amizim g…®n…®ghn…®gh…®va, ziar ekiam a dan…®ngam. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar an ziam fam.
